# Task 6: Stacked Area Chart Analysis

## Objective

Analyze cumulative app growth over time using a Stacked Area Chart in Power BI.

## Tools & Technologies

* Power BI
* DAX
* Date Table

## Steps Performed

* Created cumulative DAX measures.
* Built a Stacked Area Chart.
* Applied time-based filtering.
* Added interactive slicers.
* Analyzed category-wise growth trends over time.

## Output

A Power BI dashboard displaying cumulative installs and growth trends across app categories.

## Files Included

* Power BI (.pbix)
* Dashboard Screenshots

